         <div>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">apprehensively (?) he wil rise </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">helping me to teach and protect the child </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">making him roam in (expand) (the virtue) humanity [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] repenting </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">when there is a mistake, being able to change </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">not bringing up wind (criticism?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">and at the same time (?) bringing up a different (disloyal? reformed?) hear-mind </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">bringing up [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en">living separate but having the same desires, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en">amply flowing all under heaven </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en">nobdy will fear (him) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en">if he has a bad heart-mind </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en">nobdy will change it </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en">if women and children (or: your child?) will weep (?) [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en">if my child (=you?) will be strong, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en">steps slowly must ?? oppose (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en">sun and moon will shine </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en">looking (?) one should not be deceived (?) thrice (?) </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en">the great road, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en">all (?) maple trees (?) and mulberry trees (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en">consider my child (=you?) being fast growing (??) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en">being able to help me in return (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en">can hope to accomplish that (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en">being able to pull up (bend) for me the summit of the mulberry tree </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
